Posts.Content: The fact that you breast is cool and not red is a good sign as far as the goose bumps what you want to look at is something that looks like Orange Peel. Hold you breast in your hands and look in the mirror if you see orange peel get it looked at as for a ultrasound or mri as Inflammatory Lobular breast cancer is not found by a mammogram. They did not find mine until it turned into ductal carsinoma. After finding it was 8 cm in size.
